text: Mitrella inesitae is a species of sea snail in the family Columbellidae, the dove snails. ==Distribution== The species is endemic to the island of São Tomé, São Tomé e Príncipe.Rolán E. 2005. Columbellidae (Gastropoda, Neogastropoda) of the gulf of Guinea with the description of eight new species.
